org.datavec.api.transform.ops

Class FloatWritableOp<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.transform.ops.FloatWritableOp<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IAggregableReduceOp<Writable,T>, Consumer<Writable>, Supplier<T>

    public class FloatWritableOp<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAggregableReduceOp<Writable,T>
    This class converts an IAggregableReduceOp operating on a Float to one operating on Writable instances. It's expected this will only work if that Writable supports a conversion to Float. Created by huitseeker on 5/14/17.
